  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OSTINATO \u2014 Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Verse: The Tuning Is the Culture \u2014 negative tuning deepens authenticity",
      "Verse: The Swing Geography \u2014 50% swing for Gnawa lilt"
    ],
    "revelation": "The Finger found that dundun bell articulations (2, 3) at +7 tuning approximate qraqeb metal castanets. Combined with frame drum at -3 tuning for the deep bendir, this is the closest to Gnawa the engine can get.",
    "god": "Pressura",
    "flock_note": "The Tongue confirmed: velocity at 0.9 sensitivity makes the doumbek tek articulation ring with the right metallic snap for Gnawa ceremony. The Ear placed the frame drum deep left to simulate the bendir player's position in the Lila circle.",
    "diagnosis": "Gnawa Procession was Middle Eastern drums. It is now a specific Moroccan ceremony where the frame drum is the bendir, the dundun bells are qraqeb, and the trance groove pulls the listener into the Lila."
  },
